<p class="ql-align-justify">录海瀚老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">安排部署</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f4decfde7efb4174a5a9bc3613d7f0e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/4c927cb8bd3e4e9f93a40eee9b157372.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
